name: //ip//src
description: The IP address that initiated the request.

name: //time//receipt
description: The time when an event occurs.

name: //url//request
description: In the case of an HTTP request, this field contains the first line of the request. The request should contain the protocol and http verb.

name: //url//resource
description: In the case of an HTTP request, this field contains the resource that was requested by the client.

name: //bytes//output
description: The size of the response in bytes

name: //url//referrer
description: The previous site visited by the user. This site provided a link to the current site.
